00:18:42.506 --> 00:18:43.922
Oo naman.

00:18:43.922 --> 00:18:48.284
Makinig, si Matsuri ay nakababatang kapatid na babae ng lahat.

00:18:48.284 --> 00:18:53.460
Sige, kukuha ako ng inumin
para sa cute little Matsuri, okay?

00:18:55.827 --> 00:18:57.243
Huwag mo siyang hawakan.

00:18:57.243 --> 00:18:58.694
Okay.

00:18:58.694 --> 00:19:00.703
Mabilis din akong pumitas ng mga bulaklak.

00:19:00.703 --> 00:19:02.349
Azusa, huwag kang lalapit sa kanya.

00:19:02.349 --> 00:19:04.396
Naiintindihan ko na.

00:19:13.685 --> 00:19:15.618
Paumanhin tungkol doon.

00:19:16.422 --> 00:19:21.472
