Huh? Teka.

00:22:08.202 --> 00:22:12.847
Paumanhin. Masyado bang malakas ang boses ko kanina?

00:22:13.630 --> 00:22:15.766
Magandang gabi.

00:22:17.327 --> 00:22:19.407
Magandang gabi.

00:22:27.398 --> 00:22:30.493
Ano ba kasing ginagawa ko?

00:22:30.493 --> 00:22:33.309
Masyado lang siyang malapit...

00:22:35.771 --> 00:22:37.122
Sundin ang aking pahiwatig.

00:22:37.122 --> 00:22:39.419
Lima, anim, pito, walo, at ngayon!

00:22:39.419 --> 00:22:41.227
Dalawa, tatlo, apat...

00:22:41.227 --> 00:22:43.001
kaunti pa.

00:22:48.005 --> 00:22:50.320
Mula noong gabi ng party,

00:22:50.320 --> 00:22:56.020
nagsimula ang mga kapatid ko ng matinding pagsasanay
para sa kanilang live performance.

00:22:56.687 --> 00:23:01.297
Para silang
ibang tao, napakasipag...

00:23:02.631 --> 00:23:07.219
at sobrang intense kaya napangiwi ako...

00:23:17.295 --> 00:23:18.535
pasensya na po!

00:23:18.535 --> 00:23:20.935
- Ayos ka lang ba?
- Oo!

00:23:26.692 --> 00:23:29.265
anong mali?

00:23:29.265 --> 00:23:32.779
Kakilala ko siya, itong babaeng ito.

00:23:32.779 --> 00:23:35.521
Oh? Isang dating kasintahan?

00:23:35.521 --> 00:23:38.315
Hindi, hindi, hindi naman.

00:23:38.315 --> 00:23:42.221
Well, kung kailangan kong sabihin...

00:23:42.221 --> 00:23:48.151
Para akong ideal kuya niya.

